Saudis Give Man Lashes, Jail for Meeting Woman Alone, Sabq Says

-- B y   V i v i a n   S a l a m a
-- 
2011-03-29T12:13:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-29/saudis-give-man-lashes-jail-for-meeting-woman-alone-sabq-says.html
Saudi Arabian authorities sentenced
an Egyptian doctor to 500 lashes and five years in prison for
being in an apartment alone with a woman,  Saudi Arabia ’s Sabq
newspaper  reported today .  The incident took place last year, according to the report.
The doctor, who wasn’t identified, was arrested by police who
are responsible for “the protection of virtue and the
prevention of vice,” Sabq said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Vivian Salama in  Abu Dhabi  at 
 vsalama@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net . 